{"tid":2371304,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍拖拍到好似比人監控咁 好攰","createTime":"2021-01-18T17:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T13:05:37.000Z","uid":227608,"like":15,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"06e0555d23795884af77dedd3dcd755139805197","tid":2371304,"uid":227608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T17:15:17.000Z","msg":"次次出街都要報告去邊同邊個去係基本<br />\n但係一做少一兩次就會嬲鳩 <br />\n一野就認定你<span class=\"red\">出軌偷食</span><br />\n講嘢單單打打 又講到自己唔想對我生活冇知情權<br />\n但係知唔知情侶私人空間都有界線<br />\n有時真係想出去行下 即興約frd咁又唔係啲咩<br />\n冇乜呢個未必報備啦<br />\n屌 依家成日都質疑我出街就係偷食<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">好𠹌攰呀屌你老母</span>"},{"pid":"9e4e6f7d08edd0ec7c8a4c169a3b0f837959da03","tid":2371304,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T17:15:49.000Z","msg":"真係出俾佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34dbe3e05d8ad339ed6b63d1322e40896b706e1","tid":2371304,"uid":227608,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9e4e6f7d08edd0ec7c8a4c169a3b0f837959da03","tid":2371304,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T17:15:49.000Z","msg":"真係出俾佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T17:17:38.000Z","msg":"同佢一齊好似同其他人出個街都會不自覺咁心虛<br />\n但係明明冇做錯野"},{"pid":"0248585737671cb23d719adc381526f946994b11","tid":2371304,"uid":263198,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T17:17:56.000Z","msg":"咁辛苦<br />\n飛左佢"},{"pid":"efb1518c1489b737253ca1ac5f3817294153c054","tid":2371304,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d34dbe3e05d8ad339ed6b63d1322e40896b706e1","tid":2371304,"uid":227608,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9e4e6f7d08edd0ec7c8a4c169a3b0f837959da03","tid":2371304,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T17:15:49.000Z","msg":"真係出俾佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T17:17:3